  "id": "RAW_f07e83",
  "title": "腾讯悄悄上线了“Claude Code”，居然还支持微信登录。",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzIyMzA5NjEyMA==&mid=2647674948&idx=1&sn=65794d618744b81526644989a94f6ce5",
  "date": "2025-09-10 01:31:00",
  "author": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "siteName": "数字生命卡兹克",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">昨晚，腾讯发了他们的CodeBuddy Code，正式也加入命令行编程Agent战场。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">说实话，CodeBuddy这产品，真的有点玄学在身上的。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我之前就当个新闻写，写了两次，一次插件，一次IDE，两次都快10w+，尼玛。。。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191268\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.2074074074074074\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b260f688&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeTFps2EBQY65ibnRaYGe83gfKHXOsrRMh3ShDaw156fqFToDgxhSQtNlw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">给我整不会了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后，昨晚，他们悄悄上线了“Claude Code”，也就是CodeBuddy Code。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191270\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5574074074074075\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"2097\" data-height=\"1168\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0fe29f9c&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeTCBFg2WTib6Xfpkhc6SChTsx13tmYX1JUb9iaW51PHtU2cxibrFSeZHIWg%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <div>\n   <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我说实话，腾讯在这个节点，发了他们的编程Agent产品，这个节奏是真的挺懂的。</span></span></p>\n  </div>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我现在举双手双脚支持国产编程Agent产品，主要还是因为那个智障Anthropic。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191269\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.3190578158458244\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"934\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" type=\"block\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=91b9282a&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeToMHWtZwXIRCeGbtW3Mm8YWlFsLsYEzkf9u3aQAPths99FwSXQsPrGQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Claude Code确实好用，但是吧，我只能说，我个人单方面制裁Claude。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">真的，有些东西，还是得靠我们自己发展起来。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">腾讯他们给这个产品的定位，就是AI CLI。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191271\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.562962962962963\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1080\" data-height=\"608\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=3179c8bc&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeTH0aVyPeIk9makIrcTmr3DMCFLn7NVVo4c7iaPiczUtJmd2BR9h0nkt8Q%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">CLI（Command-line interface</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">）就是命令行的意思。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">AI CLI，说白了，就是把编程Agent放进命令行，跟Claude Code一个性质。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">你在命令行里面用最自然的语言告诉它你要干啥，它就会自动帮你完成后续的一系列动作，从生成代码、安装依赖、运行测试到自动debug，就全都一步到位了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">本来我就想用Claude Code搓一个小东西，只不过一直还没来得及，正好，这次就直接扔到CodeBuddy Code上，看看它的水平行不行。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我的任务，是用CodeBuddy Code造个能调用Nano banana的MCP，有了这个MCP，其实我就能在所有的支持MCP的软件里用上banana了，实现一句话就能完成复杂的图片处理任务，扔掉所有的P图软件。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">本来想给昨天发的即梦图片4.0也搓一个的，但是火山上还没上他们的API，有点可惜。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">我安装好CodeBuddy之后，选了国内版，基模用DeepSeek，没用Claude，直接对CodeBuddy说了一句：</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Egbodai6Oot3uSx006PcdsgOnhY&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;我直接对CodeBuddy说：&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+f&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7402251362761162756&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;2a22d9dc-a4bd-48c4-ae69-836c5c875e41&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:18,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:15},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;GGPEdtAdMoRPNHxg87fcimMEnkg&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">\"做一个生成图片用的mcp sever，用户可以调用它生成图片，可以传入图片进行图片编辑任务。调用的模型是gemini-2.5-flash-image-preview。用python开发，参考代码：<a href=\"https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/image-generation?hl=zh-cn\" target=\"_blank\">https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/image-generation?hl=zh-cn</a></span><a class=\"wx_topic_link\" topic-id=\"mfcls32h-xgzbzf\" style=\"color: #576B95 !important;\" data-topic=\"1\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">#python</span></a><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;font-weight: bold;\">\"</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Egbodai6Oot3uSx006PcdsgOnhY&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;\\&quot;做一个生成图片用的mcp sever，用户可以调用它生成图片，可以传入图片进行图片编辑任务。调用的模型是gemini-2.5-flash-image-preview。用python开发，参考代码：https://ai.google.dev/gemini-api/docs/image-generation?hl=zh-cn#python\\&quot;&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+2r*0*1+1y*0+1&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7402251362761162756&quot;],&quot;1&quot;:[&quot;link-id&quot;,&quot;0f1f192e-d2a1-4aaa-bfbb-92c3ba5c2fec&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:2}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;8d21f90b-7668-4fd9-bfe8-d8a9ee63fd56&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:19,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:170},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;CCWIdJS4LokXYtxNcbfcSkhIn9W&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">CodeBuddy开始嘟嘟嘟地干活了，它列了一个详细的计划，感觉还是挺靠谱的。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191295\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1892\" data-height=\"1424\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=addc9a12&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeTNPaHwK142p19hWFmvsCPiaibeOiaO64hr1g8RBYvBz8Q4tiaSRTrLJibx6w%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-data=\"{&quot;rootId&quot;:&quot;Egbodai6Oot3uSx006PcdsgOnhY&quot;,&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;initialAttributedTexts&quot;:{&quot;text&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;CodeBuddy开始嘟嘟嘟地干活了。它列了一个详细的计划，非常靠谱。&quot;},&quot;attribs&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:&quot;*0+z&quot;}},&quot;apool&quot;:{&quot;numToAttrib&quot;:{&quot;0&quot;:[&quot;author&quot;,&quot;7402251362761162756&quot;]},&quot;nextNum&quot;:1}},&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;referenceRecordMap&quot;:{},&quot;extra&quot;:{&quot;channel&quot;:&quot;saas&quot;,&quot;isEqualBlockSelection&quot;:true,&quot;pasteRandomId&quot;:&quot;3bab9200-6bd0-45d1-a461-5f87e83cf420&quot;,&quot;mention_page_title&quot;:{},&quot;external_mention_url&quot;:{}},&quot;isKeepQuoteContainer&quot;:false,&quot;isFromCode&quot;:false,&quot;selection&quot;:[{&quot;id&quot;:20,&quot;type&quot;:&quot;text&quot;,&quot;selection&quot;:{&quot;start&quot;:0,&quot;end&quot;:35},&quot;recordId&quot;:&quot;C7wOdKyyUodFn8xRvrIc50Z9n6b&quot;}],&quot;payloadMap&quot;:{},&quot;isCut&quot;:false}\" data-lark-record-format=\"docx/text\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">然后我就去开会去了。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\">大概不到15分钟，我回来收菜，发现，一个功能齐全的MCP服务就搭好了。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"500191296\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.7527777777777778\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"height: auto !important;\" data-width=\"1892\" data-height=\"1424\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=df7296fb&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FOjgKEXmLURom5kzM2picWWDl4iafaz4HeTwfcyZUWkqcWQjdVEF9Jz6pdsKo1TDHYDWztFkGKBs6f3ib7LhItQRzQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\" style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\"><span data-lark-record-format=\"docx/record\"></span></p>\n  <p style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right